    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/343aede7d8e3ef541b3e3ffe04d5d2a2.avif?t=1739245169\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Zen Golf is a relaxing mini golf experience with a beautiful atmosphere &amp; over <strong>180</strong> unique holes featuring all the mini golf classics plus portals, raging rivers, &amp; gusty winds! Play alone with state of the art AI or with up to <strong>20</strong> friends! Get lost in the gorgeous zen gardens &amp; all original Japanese lo-fi soundtrack!<br><br>Aimed at doing things differently, rather than the over the top and in your face insanity of other titles, Zen Golf is a calm and enjoyable experience while still maintaining that fun quirky course design that mini golf is known for. Including a whole host of unique and fun features Zen Golf is a beautiful, challenging, and rewarding experience unlike any other mini golf title.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/12fef8911606428cbc8a60ba17af51d0.poster.avif?t=1739245169\" width=640 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/12fef8911606428cbc8a60ba17af51d0.webm?t=1739245169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/12fef8911606428cbc8a60ba17af51d0.mp4?t=1739245169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u><strong>FEATURES:</strong></u><br>180+ holes across 20+ courses<br><br>Multiplayer up to 20 players<br><br>Local multiplayer only requires one controller or mouse/keyboard, the perfect party game!<br><br>1+ hour of all original Japanese lo-fi hip-hop. With music as beautiful and relaxing as the atmosphere you'll never want to leave!<br><br>Loads of customization options, every player is sure to find something that suites their personality!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/85a8697608f34333a96581134eee52a4.poster.avif?t=1739245169\" width=640 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/85a8697608f34333a96581134eee52a4.webm?t=1739245169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/85a8697608f34333a96581134eee52a4.mp4?t=1739245169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Prefer to play alone? State of the art AI opponents play differently every game, creating a unique and fun experience even for solo players.<br><br>Beautiful hand-crafted levels, each with their own garden. A delightful atmosphere you could dream of being lost in.<br><br>Super optimized graphics allowing for great performance even on low end systems. Run beautiful graphics even on laptops with integrated graphics!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/2527521795d8f2ac9c91843f8e225901.poster.avif?t=1739245169\" width=640 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/2527521795d8f2ac9c91843f8e225901.webm?t=1739245169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124690/extras/2527521795d8f2ac9c91843f8e225901.mp4?t=1739245169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
